Short:    ChopLifter 3D V0.18
Uploader: david.ellison3@ukonline.co.uk (Dave Ellison)
Author:   paul.spijkerman@ddimedia.com (Paul Spijkerman)
Type:     game/shoot


   This is kind of a Helicopter fligth simulator based on
   the old Commodore 64 game "ChopLifter" but in 3d and
   True Color.

   It can run on every machine with KS 2.04, and OCS or better.
   It can run in 16 colors, HAM6, HAM8 or Cybergraphics.

